name: Mitch
text: You did better than I thought you had in you.

name: Mitch
text: Seems like you aren't using some jarred sauce after all.

name: Mitch
text: But, I doubt your sauce is anywhere near my family's secrete recipe.

name: mitch
text: If you aren't gonna leave this basement until I give you a proper thrashing.

name: mitch
text: Then I'm just gonna have to put you in the wall like the others.
